  "text": "Ears were immersed in mRNAlater solution (Applied Biosystems) and kept at оА≤80¬∞C, and then homogenized using Tissue Lyser II (QIAGEN) and total mRNA was purified using the Fibrous Mini kit (QIAGEN). After reverse transcription into cDNA using the Reverse Transcription kit (QIAGEN), PCR was performed on a Viia7 RT-PCR detection system (Applied Biosystems). Full-length versus оБДtm Il15ra mRNA was assessed using RT-PCR, whereas levels of all other cytokines were determined via quantitative RT-PCR using SYBR Green supermix (QIAGEN). The sequences of specific primers (from Microsynth) were as follows: Il15 forward, 5оАє-CATCCATCTCGTGCTACTTGTG-3оАє; Il15 reverse, 5оАє-GCCTCT-GTTTTAGGGAGACCT-3оАє; full-length Il15ra forward, 5оАє-ATGGCCT-CGCCGCAG-3оАє; full-length Il15ra reverse, 5оАє-TTAGGCTCCTGT-GTCTTCATC-3оАє; оБДtm Il15ra forward, 5оАє-ATGGCCTCGCCGCAG-3оАє; оБДtm Il15ra reverse, 5оАє-GGACTTGTGACTGCCTGTCC-3оАє; Il17 forward, 5оАє-TTGGAGGCAGACACCCACC-3оАє; Il17 reverse, 5оАє-GATAGCGGTCC-TCATCCGTG-3оАє; Il22 forward, 5оАє-ATACATCGTCAACCGCACCTTT-3оАє; Il22 reverse, 5оАє-AGCCGGACATCTGTGTTGTTAT-3оАє; Il23p19 forward, 5оАє-TATCCAGTGTGAAGATGGTTGTG-3оАє; Il23p19 reverse, 5оАє-CACTA-AGGGCTCAGTCAGAGTTG-3оАє; Tnfa forward, 5оАє-TGTAGCCCACGT-CGTAGCAAA-3оАє; Tnfa reverse, 5оАє-CTGGCACCACTAGTTGGTTGT-3оАє. Gene expression was normalized using the ribosomal protein L27 (RPL27) housekeeping gene and data are represented as fold differences by the 2 оА≤оБДоБДCt method, with оБДCt = Ct target gene оА≤ Ct Rpl27 , and оБДоБДCt = оБДCt induced оА≤ оБДCt reference , as previously published [CITATION_1] .",
